ROSS RIVER VIRUS, MILITARY EXERCISES: AUSTRALIA
***********************************************
Date: Sat., July 19, 1997 21:03:18 MDT
From: Linda Hueston <lindah@CIDM.WSAHS.NSW.GOV.AU>
[The following report was sent to ProMED-mail 19 July, with the request that
it be not posted until clearance was obtained from Communicable Disease
Intelligence (Australia) to which a more complete report has been submitted
for publication. That permission has been granted, so we now post this very
interesting report. Obviously, the governmental organizations and individuals
involved in these studies have done a fine job of planning and follow-up. --
Mod CHC]
