e-mail: <lindah@CIDM.WSAHS.NSW.GOV.AU>
[This is a wonderfully direct approach to serodiagnosis; IgM antibody-capture
ELISA as the screening technique and neutralization for confirmation. Anyone
in the U.S. have information about imported RRV infections/cases? With the
large number of U.S. troops involved, surely there was at least one. -- Mod
CHC]
